Rem **************************
Rem *** Variables globales ***
Rem **************************

Global RoverX,RoverY,ImageID

RoverX = 100
RoverY = 100
ImageID = 1

Rem **************************
Rem *** Parametres de base ***
Rem **************************

Screen Open 0,320,200,16,Lowres
Curs Off
Flash Off
Cls 2
Hide On

Rem **************************
Rem ***       Icones       ***
Rem **************************
Get Icon Palette 1

Colour 0,$FA4
Colour 1,$AAA
Colour 2,$AAA
Colour 3,$AAA
Colour 4,$AAA
Colour 5,$FA4
Colour 6,$000
Colour 7,$000
Colour 8,$000
Colour 9,$000
Colour 10,$000
Colour 12,$000
Colour 13,$000
Colour 14,$000
Colour 15,$000
Colour 16,$000

Paste Icon 100,100,1

Rem **************************
Rem ***       Sprites      ***
Rem **************************
Set Sprite Buffer 256

Rem --- Palette BOB personnalisée ---
Get Sprite Palette 0
Colour 0,$000
Colour 1,$000
Colour 2,$FA4
Colour 3,$888
Colour 4,$AAA
Colour 5,$DDD
Colour 6,$555
Colour 7,$000
Colour 8,$000
Colour 9,$000
Colour 10,$000
Colour 12,$000
Colour 13,$000
Colour 14,$000
Colour 15,$000
Colour 16,$000

Rem --- Affiche le BOB hardware numéro 1 ---
Bob 1,RoverX,RoverY,ImageID

Rem **************************
Rem *** Boucle principale  ***
Rem **************************

While 1
    Wait Vbl

    If Key State(79) : RoverX = RoverX - 2 : ImageID = 2
    Else If Key State(78) : RoverX = RoverX + 2 : ImageID = 1
    Else If Key State(76) : RoverY = RoverY - 2
    Else If Key State(77) : RoverY = RoverY + 2
    Else If Key State(69) : End
    End If

    Rem --- Repositionne le BOB ---
    Bob 1,RoverX,RoverY,ImageID

Wend

End
